<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <%- include('partials/head'); %>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar'); %>
  <div class="container">
    <section id="docs">
      <header class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h1 class="display-2 py-2 text-xs-center text-sm-left">
            <%= title %>
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 hidden">
          <h2>Docs</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-stretch">
          <nav class="navbar navbar-expand navbar-light bg-light mb-0 w-100">
            <ul class="navbar-nav w-100 justify-content-around">
              <% for(var i=0; i < sections.length; i++) { %>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#<%= sections[i].id %>"><%= sections[i].id %></a></li>
              <% } %>
            </ul>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </header>
      <br>
      <p>
        In "Classified-ads-48", we organise posts in three sections, where you can search and also post after logging using only your email. Sections are Donations, skills and blogs.
      </p>
      <p>
        The website itself is not a business entity; This is why we add no Advertisements and it is totally free to use. We could become a business entity in future. 
      </p>
    </section>

    <% for(var i=0; i < sections.length; i++) { %>
      <h3 id="<%= sections[i].id %>"><%= sections[i].id %></h3>
      <p><%- sections[i].html %></p>
    <% } %>
    <%- include('partials/footer'); %>
  </div>
  <%- include('partials/prepare_js_variables'); %>
</body>
<%- include('partials/afterbody'); %>

</html>